<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box;">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>Mission en retard - OptiRH</title>
	</head>

	<body style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f6f6f6; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
		<table class="body-wrap" width="100%" bgcolor="#f6f6f6" style="margin: 0; padding: 0;">
			<tr>
				<td></td>
				<td class="container" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
					<div class="content" style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; border: 3px solid #e74c3c;">
						<table width="100%">
							<tr>
								<td style="text-align: center;">
									<a href="{{ absolute_url('home') }}" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 20px;">
										<img src="https://i.ibb.co/6cj94cTM/Opti-RH-finale.png" alt="OptiRH" height="80"/>
									</a>
									<h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px; color: #e74c3c;">Alerte : Mission en retard</h2>
								</td>
							</tr>
							<tr>
								<td style="padding-top: 30px;">
									<p>Bonjour
										<strong>{{ user.nom }}</strong>,</p>
									<p>La mission suivante est en retard de
										<strong style="color: #e74c3c;">{{ daysLate }}
											jour(s)</strong>
										:</p>

									<div style="background: #fdf6ee; border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
										<h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px; color: #e74c3c; font-size: 18px; text-align: center;">{{ mission.titre }}</h3>
										<p>
											<strong>Projet :</strong>
											{{ mission.getProjectTitle() }}</p>
										<p>
											<strong>Statut :</strong>
											{{ mission.status }}</p>
										<p>
											<strong>Date d'échéance :</strong>
											{{ mission.dateTerminer|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
										<p>
											<strong>Jours de retard :</strong>
											<span style="color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold;">{{ daysLate }}
												jour(s)</span>
										</p>
									</div>

									<p>Veuillez prendre les mesures nécessaires pour terminer cette mission dès que possible.</p>

									<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
										<a href="{{ url('gs-projet_project_missions_index', {id: mission.id}) }}" style="background-color: #e74c3c; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">Accéder à la mission</a>
									</div>

									<p style="margin-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px;">
										Cordialement,<br>
										<strong>L'équipe OptiRH</strong>
									</p>
								</td>
							</tr>
						</table>
					</div>

					<div class="footer" style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
						©
						{{ "now"|date("Y") }}
						OptiRH. Tous droits réservés.
					</div>
				</td>
				<td></td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</body>
</html>
